text: Lacey Turner (born 28 March 1988) is an English actress. She is known for her playing Stacey Slater in the BBC soap opera EastEnders. She won over 30 awards for that role, including ten British Soap Awards and four National Television Awards. In 2012 she played Ellie Flint in the British television show Bedlam. In 2013-2014 she played Molly Dawes in the television show Our Girl. Turner was born in North London, England. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:English television actors Category:Award winning actors Category:Actors from London Category:Living people
